 Following is the procedure to avail Installment Scheme.

 1) Register for the HOSTEL FEE INSTALLMENT SCHEME through this link
  on or before July 10th

 3) Pay the first installment of Rs 10,000/  on or before 1st
  August 2016 through SBI E2 iCollect.

 2) Submit the iCollect receipt in your hostel office and get the mess
 card.

 3) Pay the 2nd installment of Rs 11,750/ on or before 5th
  September 2016 and submit the payment receipt in your hostel office
